Git Log - Formatting

$ [prgm]git log[/prgm] [arg]--oneline[/arg] [arg]--graph[/arg] [arg]--decorate[/arg]

  [arg]--oneline[/arg]      one line per commit (short hash + subject)
  [arg]--graph[/arg]        branch graph in the left margin
  [arg]--decorate[/arg]     show branch and tag names
  [arg]--stat[/arg]         show files changed and line counts
  [arg]--name-only[/arg]    show only changed filenames
  [arg]-p[/arg]             show full diff
